    "This need becomes even more pertinent in the tourism sector, which inherently involves interactions and engagements across diverse linguistic landscapes.",
    "The Generative Pre-trained Transformer (GPT) emerges as a pivotal technology in this context, enabling enhanced communication and interaction by leveraging its advanced language translation capabilities.",
